data.description: Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity! Become the proud owner of a magnificent Coronado Estate home nestled in the heart of Sun City. This residence the is epitome of fine living, boasting updated lighting and new paint.  Sitting on an oversized wooded lot, approximately a quarter acre, it backs onto a serene greenbelt, the home features innumerable builder upgrades including crown molding, high-end stainless steel GE Profile appliances, gleaming hardwood floors, elegant wooden shutters, an extended three-car garage, state-of-the-art water treatment system, bay windows, energy-efficient LED lighting, and much more.  Indulge in relaxation with a luxurious whirlpool bath or unwind on the tranquil screened-in patio after an active day of golf, pickleball...heck!.. you name the activity. Sun City's got it all! With a central location, you'll enjoy convenient access to three golf courses and amenity centers that you can walk to, take your golf cart or catch a ride with an agreeable neighbor.  With so many clubs - woodworking, auto, golf - the toughest decision may be what NOT to do.  The back office could be used as a fourth bedroom or versatile hobby room, and features stunning hardwood floors, catering to your specific needs.  Your choice!  Your house! Schedule a visit to explore this exquisite home at your convenience. Don't let this opportunity to make it yours slip away!
